column2: SELECT g.ra, g.dec, pz.z, pz.zErr,  g.modelMag_u, g.modelMag_g, g.modelMag_r, g.modelMag_i, g.modelMag_z,  g.dered_u, g.dered_g, g.dered_r, g.dered_i, g.dered_z,  g.extinction_u, g.extinction_g, g.extinction_r, g.extinction_i, g.extinction_z,  g.petroR5#_u, g.petroR5#_g, g.petroR5#_r, g.petroR5#_i, g.petroR5#_z,  g.petroR9#_u, g.petroR9#_g, g.petroR9#_r, g.petroR9#_i, g.petroR9#_z,  pz.lumDist, pz.absMagU, pz.absMagG, pz.absMagR, pz.absMagI, pz.absMagZ,  pz.bestFitTemplateID, pz.synthU, pz.synthG, pz.synthR, pz.synthI, pz.synthZ,   pz.kcorrU, pz.kcorrG, pz.kcorrR, pz.kcorrI, pz.kcorrZ,  pz.kcorrU0#, pz.kcorrG0#, pz.kcorrR0#, pz.kcorrI0#, pz.kcorrZ0#, g.objID FROM Galaxy AS g JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID = g.objID WHERE g.ra BETWEEN # AND #  AND g.dec BETWEEN # and #  AND pz.z BETWEEN # and # ORDER BY pz.z
